title: DL Hughley Interview and More
itunes:title: DL Hughley Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had friend to the show DL Hughley call in where he spoke about Donald Trump, the election, Tiger King and more. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to another despicable coward who killed an unarmed black man who worked as a delivery driver for DoorDash, Amazon, and other companies aka an essential worker. Also Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"


Check out DL Uncut! New episodes air Fridays at 5:00 PM PT on the Laugh Out Loud Channel on PlutoTV (ch. 428).
